<p>Each block below is broken. Write the fixed code, then explain why the original was wrong.</p>
<p><strong>Bug A</strong> — Holding SPACE should fire at a steady rate, but the Laser fires <em>every single frame</em> and floods the screen with bullets.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">if is_shooting:
    bullets.append({&quot;x&quot;: spawn_x, &quot;y&quot;: spawn_y, &quot;vx&quot;: 0, &quot;color&quot;: YELLOW, &quot;r&quot;: 2})
</code></pre>
