<h2>4 · Explain Your Lesson Code 🎥</h2>
<p>Explain the Meteor Shooter code <strong>you</strong> built. Record a short phone video (show the game running) and talk through it like you are teaching someone. Try to use these words: <strong>weapon system</strong>, <strong>cooldown</strong>, <strong>homing</strong>, <strong>combo multiplier</strong>, <strong>splash damage</strong>.</p>
<blockquote>
